&lt;li&gt;Manage and grow a pipeline of prospects while maintaining consistent communication to nurture early-stage opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceed daily, weekly, monthly metrics, including qualified meetings and pipeline contribution, while delivering a stellar customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
