&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the development and maintenance of customer-facing UIs that interface with complex, high-throughput data streaming systems across Logs Intelligence, Log Compliance, and Log Ingestion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain robust Java-based backend services and APIs that specifically feed the log management user experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively participate in the team&#39;s on-call rotation, taking on reliability work to triage and support both our APIs and our highly distributed streaming services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage agentic AI technologies and modern AI coding assistants as daily tools to accelerate and enhance the software development lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively with product managers, designers, architects, researchers, and other engineers to ship software incrementally with frequent customer feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to code reviews, evangelize engineering standards, and mentor more junior team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
