&lt;li&gt;8+ years of software engineering experience, operating as a dedicated Frontend specialist but possessing a strong, practical background in backend development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in React, TypeScript, including hooks, state management, and component-based architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
